  "detailed_description": "This is a simple brick breaker. It was made over 5 weekends by a solo dev. It was made mostly so that I could gain familiarity with the process of putting a game on Steam. If you enjoy it, great, if not let me know why and I'll take note.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Bricks that break. <br></li><li> Balls, lots of balls (They break bricks). <br></li><li> Power ups (They might break bricks). <br></li><li> Full level editor<br></li><li> and a bonus 100% extra sarcasm included in the base price. </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drops</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967970/extras/bbfbc47bf79d20aa66d29c1eb0cc1a38.avif?t=1716355744\" width=505 height=517 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/967970/extras/1314925eeba7ea56280e05f093fc199c.avif?t=1716355744\" width=539 height=511 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Next on the Roadmap:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Individual High Scores for each level set<br></li><li> Integrate level editor with Steam Workshop<br></li><li> Add more power ups<br></li><li> Localizations<br></li><li> and more ...</li></ul>",
